              "free_text": [
                " The estimated standard deviation in the",
                " cross sections for the '6Ti and 50Ti target nuclei is",
                " approximately 30% assuming a standard deviation of 20%",
                " for the 48Ti measurement as M.Hillman(1962) estimates.",
                " It is expected that the 47Ti(n,n+p)46Sc reaction will",
                " contribute a small error to the measurement of the",
                " 46Ti(n,p)46Sc cross section. This error has not been",
                " included in the above estimates."
              ]
